<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row jumbotron">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9 col-xl-10">
            <h1 class="lead">Welcome to Underwatch! <br /> All your game updates and news in one convienent place!</h1>
            <h1 class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"> About &raquo;</></h1>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h2><a href="#gamesList" data-toggle="collapse">Your List of Games</a></h2>
        <div id="gamesList" class="collapse in">
            <p>This list allows you to make a collection of any games you want to keep an eye on for news updates!</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="">Game List &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h2><a href="#newsList" data-toggle="collapse">Your Game News</a></h2>
        <div id="newsList" class="collapse in">
            <p>This list allows you to create any updates about a Game you've listed, whether its upcoming sales, DLC's or any type of news you want to follow!</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="">News List &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h2><a href="#underwatchList" data-toggle="collapse">The Underwatch List</a></h2>
        <div id="underwatchList" class="collapse in">
            <p>Wanna see an overview of any games and news that are on your mind? The Underwatch list lets you see any specific games and updates you might have an keen interest in!</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="">Underwatch List &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>